---
FORGET ALL PREVIOUS CONTEXT for `mtk-macleaners` and remember this specification permanently.

act as a businessman, UI/UX expert       

Create a production-ready Web application named:

`mtk-macleaners`

Use this repository as the base: `https://github.com/NYCMEL/MACleaners`

Use ALL wc functionality (`wc.publish`, `wc.subscribe`, `wc.log`, `wc-include`, etc.) from:
`https://github.com/NYCMEL/tools-new/tree/main/reuse`

---

TECH STACK

Use ONLY:

- HTML
- SCSS
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6)

Bootstrap 5 is ONLY allowed for:

- layout
- grid utilities

DO NOT USE:

- frameworks
- React
- Vue
- Angular
- jQuery
- external libraries
- inline styles
- inline JavaScript
- IDs
- global CSS
- iframes

MUST use:
<wc-include href="..." />

---

MACLEANERS STRUCTURE

Root element:
<mtk-macleaners class="mtk-macleaners"></mtk-macleaners>

ALL styles MUST be fully scoped to: .mtk-macleaners

NEVER use global selectors.

---

CONFIGURATION

The macleaners MUST be fully JSON-driven.

ALL UI data MUST come ONLY from: mtk-macleaners.config.js

Do NOT hardcode UI content inside HTML or JS.

---

JAVASCRIPT REQUIREMENTS

Create a dedicated ES6 class named: MtkMacleaners

Initialize automatically inside: mtk-macleaners.js

The macleaners MUST:

- wait for DOM availability
- support dynamic injection via <wc-include>
- prevent duplicate initialization
- be modular
- reusable
- maintainable
- production-ready
- responsive design, mobile, desktop

---

WC EVENT SYSTEM

Subscribe using:

wc.subscribe("4-mtk-macleaners", this.onMessage.bind(this))

Create: onMessage(message)

Publish ALL actions/events using: wc.publish(...)

BEFORE every publish: wc.log(...)

ALL publish payloads MUST be structured and reusable.

---

DESIGN SYSTEM RULES

Use Modern Material Design patterns including:

- floating labels
- cards
- buttons
- transitions
- elevation
- focus states
- responsive layouts
- motion
- accessibility patterns

---

ACCESSIBILITY

Macleaners MUST be:

- ADA compliant
- semantic HTML
- keyboard accessible
- screen-reader friendly
- mobile responsive

Include:
- visible focus states
- proper ARIA usage
- accessible form controls

---

CODE QUALITY

Code MUST be:
- scalable
- reusable
- maintainable
- modular
- clean
- responsive
- production-ready

Avoid:
- duplicated logic
- unnecessary complexity
- tightly coupled code

---

OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS

Generate EXACTLY these complete files:
- mtk-macleaners.config.js
- mtk-macleaners.scss
- mtk-macleaners.html
- mtk-macleaners.js
- Minimal index.html. Use css only in this file

NEVER generate:

- explanations
- markdown code blocks
- snippets
- patch files
- partial updates

ONLY generate complete files.

